name: angel phoenix and devil phoenix 04
description:
Confrontation of two characters: good and evil /angel and devil
My name is FERESHTEH that means ANGEL.
My personality looks alot like phoenix.
I have alot patient against of evils, persecutions and misfortunes against myself.
Phoenix is a mythical bird which is the symbol of immortality of patience and endurance and its other obvious signature is development and loneliness.
But when its patience runs out it puts all its beauty and glory and generosity away and with its loud voice that is earsplitting for some and delightful for others and setting itself on fire and all the beings who hurts it finishes that pain.
But phoenix as it knows it is Immortal and it reborns from it ashes and its all full of Patience and glory again and absolutely full of proud to gain the climax of its life after all that rage.
This collection includes 50 motion graphics, 25 various phoenix characters, in two different parts.
The first part happens on earth before tolerating all the harassment and the second one contains its apogee in the space after tolerating all things happend.
That It will be presented over time.
